            <div class="title">
                Foreign Affairs (Korea And Indo-China)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1954-06-23/debates/764873bf-75f3-4a2e-a288-1ee0c901c329/WalsallChestClinic(X-RayFacilities)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
