                Mr. John Rankin  (Glasgow, Tradeston)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-de957b31-0e6a-4115-b46c-aed9335aa2e2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
