            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-5af145ea-5926-4a5f-9b84-4ffa9c66b9fb">
                Mr. J. Hynd
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-5af145ea-5926-4a5f-9b84-4ffa9c66b9fb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
